subject: Women and Girls
Records and Achievements
Basketball (College)
Coaches and Managers
lead_paragraph: With one more victory, the Harvard women’s basketball coach Kathy Delaney-Smith would pass the former Princeton men’s coach Pete Carril for the most basketball victories by an Ivy League coach.
